abstract: To the list of problems currently dogging the Jaguars (1-3), we can now add ridicule.
snippet: To the list of problems currently dogging the Jaguars (1-3), we can now add ridicule.
lead_paragraph: To the growing list of problems currently dogging the Jaguars (1-3) -- poor play, a rookie quarterback, questionable roster moves and the specter of relocation -- we can now add a new one: ridicule. But at least this time it was not Coach Jack Del Rio's fault.

headline.main: Wait, Which Way Are the Jaguars Headed?
